        <h3 class="card-name">Jones Hole Fish Hatchery</h3>
        <p class="card-desc">A beautiful drive leads to a working fish hatchery where you can watch thousands of trout up close. From here, the Jones Hole Trail follows a stunning creek through canyon walls to Ely Creek Waterfall — one of the most rewarding hikes in the region. Kids love the fish.</p>
